@DATABASE "Skatin' USA"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Skatin' USA"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                                Skatin' USA
                                ===========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Energy = x" rxs "address command zxampoke(55475,255)"}              55475,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Ammo = x  " rxs "address command zxampoke(55493,255)"}              55493,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
